.TP
.B \-\-disable-autodiscover
disable autodiscover feature
.TP
.B \-c CLIENT, \-\-client CLIENT
connect to a Glances server by IPv4/IPv6 address or hostname
.TP
.B \-p PORT, \-\-port PORT
define the client/server TCP port [default: 61209]
.TP
.B \-\-password
